 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground h-10 px-4 py-2 transition-smooth\">Events</button></a><a href=\"/join\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground h-10 px-4 py-2 transition-smooth\">Join Us</button></a></div><div class=\"flex md:hidden items-center absolute right-4\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground h-10 w-10\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></nav><section class=\"pt-32 pb-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center animate-fade-in\"><div class=\"mb-8\"><h1 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-light-title mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">About Us</h1><div class=\"w-24 h-1 gradient-primary mx-auto mb-8\"></div></div><p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Pioneering blockchain innovation at Switzerland&#x27;s leading technical university</p></div></div></section><div class=\"w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-gray-200 to-transparent\"></div><section class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light-title mb-6 text-gray-800\">Our Mission</h2><div class=\"w-16 h-1 gradient-primary mx-auto\"></div></div><div class=\"space-y-6 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-lg\"><p>We&#x27;re the first accredited student blockchain association at ETH Zurich. Started as a student initiative, our goal is simple: plant seeds of knowledge and curiosity about blockchain technology in our peers.</p><p>What drives us? We want students to become educators themselves—sharing what they learn with classmates today and colleagues tomorrow. It&#x27;s about raising awareness beyond the hype and speculation.</p><p>This is our contribution to a better blockchain space. One with fewer scams, less noise, and more people who actually understand the fundamentals. We believe education is how we get there.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light-title mb-6 text-gray-800\">Who We Are</h2><div class=\"w-16 h-1 gradient-primary mx-auto\"></div></div><div class=\"space-y-6 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-lg\"><p>ETHBLOCKCHAIN CLUB is a student-run initiative at ETH Zurich. We&#x27;re into blockchain, cryptography, and everything decentralized.</p><p>Academic research meets real-world building here. Theory isn&#x27;t stuck in papers, and projects aren&#x27;t built in a vacuum. That&#x27;s the space we create.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light-title mb-6 text-gray-800\">Board</h2><div class=\"w-16 h-1 gradient-primary mx-auto\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><img alt=\"Jennis Bešić\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fjennis.jpeg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fjennis.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fjennis.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Jennis Bešić</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">President &amp; Founder\nBSc Computer Science</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Passionate about blockchain technology and its potential to revolutionize industries.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><img alt=\"Anej Rozman\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fanej.jpeg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fanej.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fanej.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Anej Rozman</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Head of Events &amp; Co-Founder\nMSc Quantitative Finance</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Strong believer in the longevity of blockchain technologies, crypto currencies and decentralization.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><img alt=\"Gustave Charles\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fgustave.jpeg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fgustave.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fgustave.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Gustave Charles</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Head of Recruiting and Member Organization\nMSc Cyber Security</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Working in privacy, decentralisation and governance real-world usecases.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><img alt=\"Ariele Marcellino\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fariele.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fariele.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fariele.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Ariele Marcellino</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Head of Innovation and Technology</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Lorem</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light-title mb-6 text-gray-800\">Our Poles</h2><div class=\"w-16 h-1 gradient-primary mx-auto\"></div></div><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto space-y-12\"><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-8 text-center\">Marketing</h3><div class=\"flex justify-center mb-8\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 max-w-sm\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold\">Tcby</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">This could be you!</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Lead</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Leading our marketing initiatives and community outreach efforts.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 w-64\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><img alt=\"Dominic\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fdominic.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fdominic.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fdominic.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Dominic</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Member</p></div></div></div><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-8 text-center\">External Relations</h3><div class=\"flex justify-center mb-8\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 max-w-sm\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold\">Tcby</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">This could be you!</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Lead</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Managing partnerships and external communications with industry leaders.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 w-64\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><img alt=\"Noé Macé\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fnoe.jpeg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fnoe.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fnoe.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Noé Macé</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Member</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 w-64\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold\">PG</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Pedro Gouveia</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Member</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 w-64\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><img alt=\"Ilan Nissim\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Filan.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Filan.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Filan.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Ilan Nissim</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Member</p></div></div></div><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-8 text-center\">Events</h3><div class=\"flex justify-center mb-8\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 max-w-sm\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><img alt=\"Anej Rozman\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fanej.jpeg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fanej.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fanej.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Anej Rozman</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Lead</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Organizing meetups, hackathons, and social events for our community with delicious catering.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 w-64\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold\">FD</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Firas Dridi</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Member</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 w-64\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold\">GX</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Gökhan XX</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Member</p></div></div></div><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-8 text-center\">Innovation and Technology</h3><div class=\"flex justify-center mb-8\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 max-w-sm\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><img alt=\"Ariele Marcellino\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fariele.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fariele.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fariele.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Ariele Marcellino</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Lead</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Leading the technical development of our website and additional projects.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 w-64\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><img alt=\"Cyrill\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fcyrill.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fcyrill.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fcyrill.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Cyrill</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Member</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 w-64\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold\">GH</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Gamal H</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Member</p></div></div></div><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-8 text-center\">Financial &amp; Legal</h3><div class=\"flex justify-center mb-8\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 max-w-sm\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold\">Tcby</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">This could be you!</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Lead</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Building connections with universities and the global Ethereum community.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6\"></div></div><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-8 text-center\">Recruiting &amp; Member Organization</h3><div class=\"flex justify-center mb-8\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50 max-w-sm\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><img alt=\"Gustave Charles\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fgustave.jpeg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fgustave.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fteam%2Fgustave.jpeg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Gustave Charles</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Lead</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Lorem</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light-title mb-6 text-gray-800\">Location &amp; Context</h2><div class=\"w-16 h-1 gradient-primary mx-auto\"></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-elegant relative h-64\"><img src=\"/eth-zurich-campus.jpg\" alt=\"ETH Zurich Campus - Aerial view of the main building\" class=\"object-cover\"/></div><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-center\">Based at ETH Zurich, one of the world&#x27;s leading universities for science and technology, we benefit from a rich ecosystem of innovation and research excellence. Our home in Zurich, a global hub for blockchain and cryptocurrency innovation, provides unique opportunities to engage with industry leaders, researchers, and the broader Ethereum community.</p></div></div></section><footer class=\"bg-muted/30 border-t border-border mt-20\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center space-y-4 md:col-span-2\"><div class=\"flex justify-center\"><img src=\"/ethbcc_logo.png\" alt=\"ETHBCC Logo\" class=\"h-4 w-auto\"/></div><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground text-center\">Building the future of decentralized innovation at ETH Zurich.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4 text-center md:text-left\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold\">Quick Links</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-smooth\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-smooth\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-smooth\" href=\"/events\">Events</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-smooth\" href=\"/join\">Join Us</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-smooth\" href=\"/collaborate\">Collaborate with Us</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"space-y-4 text-center md:text-left\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold\">Connect</h4><div class=\"flex justify-center md:justify-start space-x-4\"><a href=\"https://github.com/ethblockchain\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-smooth\" aria-label=\"GitHub\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-github h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4\"></path><path d=\"M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://linkedin.com/company/ethblockchain\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-smooth\" aria-label=\"LinkedIn\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-linkedin h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z\"></path><rect width=\"4\" height=\"12\" x=\"2\" y=\"9\"></rect><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></a><a href=\"mailto:contact@ethblockchain.club\" class=\"text-muted